{
  "stem": "12402.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After-- when I found my brother, we're hugging and kisses and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the farmer came up the next day-- we stayed in the barn overnight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next day-- at night they took us in to another location, to a stable of cows.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Cows were down below, and we were on top.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put us on top.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only lying accommodation.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No stand up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's a small attic there, a small place to-- to accommodate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was very tight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were lying there and didn't take long-- no, but the farmer took us down every morning for breakfast. 5 o'clock in the morning, we had a hot breakfast, potatoes and borscht and whatever he's having.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and he put us right back because he was afraid of the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anybody would find out he could get shot, burned, the whole house and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took a big chance anyway, but he kept us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there maybe I would say a month on the-- on the winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was warm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was straws around us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it-- it didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All of a sudden, my brother develops a temperature on the-- he's burning like a fire and all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He must've been 102.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every day gets worse, and I knew already that's-- that's the-- there was no doctors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's nobody, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and they gave us during the day food from the-- from the stable.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There's a hole in the-- on the top.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He gave us water, to-- lunch, whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We ate, but he was sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was maybe a week, took a week, maybe 10 days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The last few days, he was hysterical.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everything came out of his mouth white, the saliva and all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was-- it was very frightening.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
